I know him, he&#8217;s a good guy, a little bit shy<br />
Spends his life dreaming about love<br />
Because his heart asks for a little more heat</p>
<p>She came by, and her beauty caught him right away<br />
They love each other, and now he says<br />
He found life&#8217;s greatest gift, happiness</p>
<p>He thinks of her all the time<br />
Dreams of her all night long<br />
Cries for her if she doesn&#8217;t come</p>
<p>He keeps talking about her<br />
She&#8217;s all he can think of<br />
He can&#8217;t live without her</p>
